    "description": "The Premium Version of Just Act Natural is here! A one time purchase of the Premium Version gets you six all new game modes and 4 new maps! <strong>IF THE HOST HAS THE PREMIUM VERSION EVERY IN THE LOBBY HAS ACCESS TO ALL THE GAME MODES AND MAPS</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/0beeb1610679d6c4f3dfabeba61055cc.avif?t=1767648462\" width=600 height=210 /></span><br><br>In <strong>ASSASSINS</strong> all players are HIDERS and must find and kill the other players without revealing themselves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/21a5e07eee03bec0f82324bfcd00da6f.poster.avif?t=1767648462\" width=374 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/21a5e07eee03bec0f82324bfcd00da6f.webm?t=1767648462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/21a5e07eee03bec0f82324bfcd00da6f.mp4?t=1767648462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <strong>DEATH RACE</strong> Hider players must race each other to the finish line without being too eager and revealing themselves to the Seeker above!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/1f1c0454c9e0dd65db21cae4d69d0436.poster.avif?t=1767648462\" width=318 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/1f1c0454c9e0dd65db21cae4d69d0436.webm?t=1767648462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/1f1c0454c9e0dd65db21cae4d69d0436.mp4?t=1767648462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In addition, this version includes 3 more game modes, including <strong>PARTY MODE</strong>, which combines all the game modes together randomly!<br><br>Finally, the new hand-sculpted CASTLE, SPOODER MINES, STINK CITY and SPACESHIP stages have been added. Walk around as knights and wizards hiding from the Seeker placed in the MIDDLE of the stage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/6776ba2ddc7c50ac7009bbb3dff2506d.poster.avif?t=1767648462\" width=794 height=544 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/6776ba2ddc7c50ac7009bbb3dff2506d.webm?t=1767648462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740900/extras/6776ba2ddc7c50ac7009bbb3dff2506d.mp4?t=1767648462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
